<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id27fad150-2a4a-11ef-83f3-c9aca8a7e419" identifier="/us/usc/t45/s1213"><num value="1213">§ 1213.</num><heading> Conflict with other laws</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The provisions of this chapter shall govern if there is any conflict between this chapter and any other law.</p>
